		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Sparks leap between the covers of this copper-bound tome.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Implement</b><b>:</b> Tome</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +5d6 lightning critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Properties:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>When you use a wizard lightning attack power through this tome, you can score a critical hit on a roll of 19-20.</li>\n<li>This tome contains two wizard daily lightning powers. Both powers must be of a level equal to or lower than that of the tome. You must choose these powers when you acquire the tome; they can't be changed later. You can add these powers to your spellbook.</li>\n</ul></p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power âœ¦ Daily (Free Action)</b></p><p>You choose a power contained in the tome and expend an unused wizard daily attack power of an equal or higher level. You gain the use of the chosen power. The power is lost if you don't use it before</p><p>the end of the encounter</p>",
